you to get married

560
01:10:39,735 --> 01:10:41,362
We have known them for years

561
01:10:41,570 --> 01:10:43,868
And we thought we'd turn friendship
into a marriage alliance

562
01:10:45,241 --> 01:10:47,709
You don't lose anything by
meeting Pooja, do you?

563
01:10:50,379 --> 01:10:54,076
Okay. But you know my answer.
And that's NO!

564
01:11:00,222 --> 01:11:01,052
Who is it, Sameer?

565
