This is Akash and this is Sid

571
01:12:10,092 --> 01:12:11,457
Seems like a deep friendship

572
01:12:11,794 --> 01:12:14,627
Either the friendship is deep
or it's a 3-D photograph

573
01:12:32,715 --> 01:12:36,981
Pooja, you do know why
you're here, don't you?

574
01:12:38,020 --> 01:12:40,750
Yes. Mom and Dad told me

575
01:12:44,326 --> 01:12:46,317
Look, honestly speaking...

576
01:12:46,528 --> 01:12:50,259
When Mom told me about this...
l felt it wasn't right at first...

577
01:12:50,866 --> 01:12:55,166
...but now...l'm so happy you said no to
this arranged marriage bullshit!

578
01:13:01,543 --> 01:13:03,670
l think marriages shouldn't be
made like this

579
01:13:03,879 --> 01:13:06,677
lt's so important to love somebody
to get married

580
01:13:07,383 --> 01:13:08,145
What do you think?

581
01:13:08,384 --> 01:13:09,510
Yes, absolutely

582
01:13:12,388 --> 01:13:13,355
