someone?

583
01:13:26,402 --> 01:13:27,835
There is this guy in my life

584
01:13:28,237 --> 01:13:30,933
But l guess l don't love him
enough so far to marry him

585
01:13:32,074 --> 01:13:33,473
l pretty much feel the same...

586
