Look, Sameer...

592
01:14:08,777 --> 01:14:10,745
l have no doubt whatsoever
you have fallen in love with her

593
01:14:11,280 --> 01:14:13,407
But l'm equally sure that after
3 months...

594
01:14:13,615 --> 01:14:14,775
...you'll be in love with some other
girl

595
01:14:15,551 --> 01:14:16,245
No, Akash

596
01:14:18,787 --> 01:14:21,915
l always thought l knew
what love was

597
01:14:22,124 --> 01:14:23,955
l realized today that l was
completely wrong

598
01:14:24,827 --> 01:14:25,259
ls that so!

599
01:14:26,728 --> 01:14:29,595
Akash, when Pooja told me about
that guy in her life ...

600
01:14:29,798 --> 01:14:33,165
For the first time l thought about
all those girls in my life...

601
01:14:33,469 --> 01:14:34,936
l was attracted to all of them...

602
01:14:35,370 --> 01:14:37,395
But l was wrong to think
the attraction was love

603
01:14:39,641 --> 01:14:41,438
And now you love Pooja?

604
01:14:41,643 --> 01:14:46,080
Yes. That's it!
l love Pooja

605
01:14:47,149 --> 01:14:48,776
Then tell her

606
01:14:51,286 --> 01:14:54,050
Take my advice. Don't say
anything to anyone

607
01:14:54,990 --> 01:14:55,957
There's no trusting you

608
01:14:56,158 --> 01:14:57,625
Today it's Pooja,
tomorrow it'll be some Ahuja!

