611
01:15:20,582 --> 01:15:22,140
l am so happy today

612
01:15:23,519 --> 01:15:27,478
Guess what? Esha called me

613
01:15:30,859 --> 01:15:32,656
She is coming to see me today

614
01:15:34,830 --> 01:15:36,263
My daughter is coming here...

615
01:15:48,243 --> 01:15:50,507
Sid, she remembered it's
my birthday today

616
01:15:54,216 --> 01:15:57,344
l'll be seeing her after 5 years!

617
01:15:58,921 --> 01:16:01,685
l've cooked everything myself.
l baked a cake

618
01:16:03,992 --> 01:16:05,186
l'm so happy

619
01:16:05,727 --> 01:16:08,355
ls Esha coming alone or your...

620
01:16:08,797 --> 01:16:13,860
Oh no. She told him she's going to
a friend's birthday party...

621
01:16:14,236 --> 01:16:18,036
Because Ajay will never let her
come here

622
01:16:21,977 --> 01:16:22,944
Would you like to meet her?

623
01:16:25,547 --> 01:16:26,206
lt'll make me happy

624
01:16:33,922 --> 01:16:37,551
How dare you teach my daughter
to lie? Have you no shame?

625
01:16:39,928 --> 01:16:43,728
Thank God l heard Esha
talk to you over the phone

626
01:16:44,099 --> 01:16:46,067
Why don't you stay away from her?

627
01:16:46,768 --> 01:16:48,065
l am her mother!

628
01:16:48,503 --> 01:16:51,904
You were her mother but now
Kiran is her mother

629
01:16:52,608 --> 01:16:54,405
lt'd be wise of you to understand
this

630
01:16:54,943 --> 01:16:57,571
Don't ever try to meet Esha again

631
01:16:58,113 --> 01:17:00,411
Not unless you want me to take
you to court... again

632
01:17:01,783 --> 01:17:03,216
You understand what l'm getting at,
don't you?

633
01:17:45,827 --> 01:17:47,624
He tells me l am not Esha's mother!

634
01:17:47,829 --> 01:17:48,796
That Esha is not my daughter!

635
01:17:48,997 --> 01:17:55,630
l am her mother...

636
01:18:00,942 --> 01:18:02,204
He married again

637
01:18:03,345 --> 01:18:06,803
He destroyed all my dreams.
l said nothing

638
01:18:08,617 --> 01:18:10,642
Because l had everything...

639
01:18:12,721 --> 01:18:13,483
l had my Esha

640
01:18:16,591 --> 01:18:21,824
