641
01:18:22,964 --> 01:18:24,158
l have nothing at all

642
01:18:25,300 --> 01:18:33,867
l am nothing. Nothing.

643
01:18:56,598 --> 01:19:01,399
You know, crying doesn't suit
you at all

644
01:19:03,739 --> 01:19:05,206
What else can l do!

645
01:19:08,410 --> 01:19:09,707
You can come with me

646
01:20:04,566 --> 01:20:08,263
You two must be wondering where
Siddharth has brought you!

647
01:20:08,470 --> 01:20:11,098
No such thing. We'd go
anywhere to eat cake

648
01:20:18,880 --> 01:20:19,938
Will you dance with me?

649
01:20:22,184 --> 01:20:25,347
Where?
- Right here there's lot of space, come.

650
01:21:20,709 --> 01:21:21,676
Sid, we've reached your house

651
01:21:26,882 --> 01:21:28,349
What?

652
01:21:35,390 --> 01:21:36,516
You're joking, right?

653
01:21:41,563 --> 01:21:43,190
Hey Akash, he's serious man!

654
01:21:44,499 --> 01:21:45,864
Have you gone mad?

655
01:21:52,807 --> 01:21:55,207
Sid, my knowledge of such
things is a bit sad but...

656
01:21:55,911 --> 01:21:57,344
...this is a but much, isn't it?

657
01:22:00,115 --> 01:22:02,310
ls that because she's older?

658
