drinking problem

665
01:22:37,786 --> 01:22:38,912
What should we understand?
- Just this...

666
01:22:39,354 --> 01:22:41,413
l know all this and still
love her

667
01:22:42,057 --> 01:22:45,891
But Sid, think about it.
This isn't love, it's insanity

668
01:22:46,094 --> 01:22:48,756
No. This is love

669
01:22:51,800 --> 01:22:54,098
l don't expect her to be mine
or marry me

670
01:22:54,469 --> 01:22:55,766
l don't expect any such thing

671
01:22:56,771 --> 01:22:59,103
Even if she doesn't love me,
it's okay because l...

672
01:22:59,307 --> 01:23:02,606
okay! l get it

673
