Remember, Sameer? Even l had
started off like this

674
01:23:07,916 --> 01:23:11,374
Started what off?
Oh. Of course.

675
01:23:11,586 --> 01:23:15,454
Okay, Sid. lf that's what it's about
then l have no objection

676
01:23:16,091 --> 01:23:17,786
ln fact she's perfect for you

677
01:23:18,193 --> 01:23:22,459
She's experienced, lives alone.
You visit her everyday

678
01:23:24,265 --> 01:23:26,460
Learn from him, Sameer

679
01:23:26,801 --> 01:23:29,133
Really, Sid. You couldn't have
chosen better...

680
01:23:34,075 --> 01:23:35,975
How disgusting can you get!

681
01:23:39,147 --> 01:23:43,345
Here l am telling you l love her and
you make it sound so sick and dirty

682
01:23:48,490 --> 01:23:51,152
We don't have to approve
everything our friends do

683
01:23:52,660 --> 01:23:54,992
But there is a line in every
friendship that shouldn't be crossed

684
01:23:55,196 --> 01:23:56,629
And you have crossed it today

685
01:24:02,037 --> 01:24:05,939
At some point in life everyone
experiences true love

686
01:24:08,143 --> 01:24:11,670
Then all the things you said...
about her age and stuff...

687
01:24:13,314 --> 01:24:17,375
They don't mean anything.
They all seem trivial

688
01:24:21,289 --> 01:24:22,779
You won't understand this today

689
01:24:25,560 --> 01:24:26,857
But some day you will know...

690
01:24:27,062 --> 01:24:28,927
You don't decide to fall in love

691
01:24:30,698 --> 01:24:31,665
lt just happens

692
01:24:38,573 --> 01:24:39,699
Are you finished?

693
01:24:49,918 --> 01:24:50,748
Sameer, are you coming?

694
01:25:46,474 --> 01:25:47,736
l still remember that night

695
01:25:55,884 --> 01:25:58,182
l never thought things would go
that far

696
01:26:04,592 --> 01:26:05,684
l couldn't sleep all night

697
01:26:07,262 --> 01:26:08,752
l went and met Akash
the next morning

698
01:26:48,703 --> 01:26:50,534
These things happen
between friends

699
01:26:51,005 --> 01:26:54,338
Let's go meet Sid.
He must be feeling bad too

700
01:26:56,611 --> 01:26:58,511
You're sure to run into him
somewhere

701
01:26:58,913 --> 01:27:01,711
What'll you do? lgnore him?

702
01:27:08,323 --> 01:27:09,517
You're coming to meet Sid

703
01:27:12,060 --> 01:27:13,186
Leave me alone, Sameer!

704
01:27:39,787 --> 01:27:40,754
l have to see Sid

705
01:27:41,089 --> 01:27:41,987
He's gone

706
01:27:42,190 --> 01:27:43,953
Where? - Kasauli

707
01:27:44,359 --> 01:27:49,228
They called yesterday to say his
application was accepted. So he...

708
01:27:52,233 --> 01:27:55,532
What is it, Sameer?
ls everything alright?

709
01:27:57,772 --> 01:28:00,639
Of course. l should go

710
01:28:07,682 --> 01:28:10,981
l didn't realise that things
would never be the same again

711
01:28:11,886 --> 01:28:16,289
You went to Kasauli...A week later,
Akash left for Australia

712
01:28:27,902 --> 01:28:29,130
Take care of yourself

713
01:28:29,671 --> 01:28:32,834
You remember the name of the man
who'll receive you in Sydney?

714
01:28:33,041 --> 01:28:36,169
Mr.Mehta...Relax, Dad.
l remember

715
01:28:41,816 --> 01:28:44,011
Bye. l'll call you from there

716
01:28:47,655 --> 01:28:49,589
l must tell you something
-What's it?

717
01:28:51,526 --> 01:28:58,398
l always made fun of your
endless romantic entanglements

718
01:29:00,601 --> 01:29:03,968
Never stopped to think how you
must feel

719
01:29:06,274 --> 01:29:09,437
You know l was just kidding,
don't you?

720
01:29:13,147 --> 01:29:14,171
Don't worry about it

721
01:29:14,849 --> 01:29:16,248
You weren't the only one who was
kidding

722
01:29:17,785 --> 01:29:18,877
You remember Shalini?

723
01:29:20,355 --> 01:29:22,846
l remember Shalini...
And Rohit's punch as well

724
01:29:24,258 --> 01:29:25,987
l knew she was Rohit's fiancee

725
01:29:28,262 --> 01:29:30,287
Why didn't you tell me?
Why didn't you stop me?

726
01:29:57,759 --> 01:29:58,691
l said Hi

727
01:30:02,563 --> 01:30:03,495
Where are you going?

728
01:30:05,400 --> 01:30:06,833
This flight goes to Sydney

729
01:30:07,568 --> 01:30:08,592
But where are you going?

730
01:30:11,406 --> 01:30:13,567
How strange! All three of us
are going to Sydney

731
01:30:14,809 --> 01:30:15,275
Three?

732
01:30:15,676 --> 01:30:17,337
Sure. You, me, and this flight

733
01:30:21,582 --> 01:30:23,174
You do know you're insane,
don't you?

734
01:30:31,926 --> 01:30:34,861
l'm really sorry about
the other night

735
01:30:36,431 --> 01:30:37,329
l was just kidding

736
01:30:45,907 --> 01:30:46,396
So what are you...

737
01:30:50,244 --> 01:30:51,768
What are you doing in Sydney?

738
01:30:52,847 --> 01:30:55,475
Dad has a business there he
wants me to manage...

739
01:30:56,184 --> 01:30:59,085
Let's see how long it lasts now.
And you?

740
01:31:00,221 --> 01:31:01,381
My uncle lives there

741
01:31:01,823 --> 01:31:04,121
My mother's brother.
l'm visiting him

742
01:31:04,659 --> 01:31:05,557
He's nothing like Rohit, is he!

743
01:31:09,997 --> 01:31:10,656
What does he do?

744
01:31:14,402 --> 01:31:15,596
Have you been to Sydney before?

745
01:31:17,738 --> 01:31:19,296
Do you always ask so many
questions?

746
01:31:19,841 --> 01:31:22,139
Yes. Have you been to Sydney
before?

747
01:31:22,944 --> 01:31:23,410
Yes

748
01:31:24,979 --> 01:31:26,378
Good. You can show me around

749
01:31:26,914 --> 01:31:30,145
Wait a minute. Don't you know
anybody else there?

750
01:31:30,985 --> 01:31:32,213
Of course. There is a Mr.Mehta

751
01:31:34,055 --> 01:31:36,023
And won't it be fun hanging out
with him?

752
01:31:40,661 --> 01:31:41,559
l said l'm sorry

753
01:31:42,296 --> 01:31:44,526
Okay but l will have to ask
my uncle

754
01:31:46,701 --> 01:31:48,293
But he won't refuse.

755
01:31:48,936 --> 01:31:49,402
Why?

756
01:31:50,171 --> 01:31:51,433
Because l have bought him a gift!

757
01:32:24,205 --> 01:32:26,366
l'm fine but please stop
